The paper introduces a new neural network architecture for reinforcement learning, which falls under the category of machine learning and artificial intelligence. The use of genetic algorithms also suggests a focus on optimization and search algorithms, which could fall under robotics or systems engineering. Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.RO (Robotics).
